---
import HeadingPath from "../blog/HeadingPath.astro"
---


<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter items-start max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-10">

  <!-- Left Article Container -->
  <article class="lg:col-span-8 w-full max-w-4xl">

    <!-- Title Section -->
    <header class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6">

        <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary border border-primary/20 px-3 py-1 font-label-xs text-label-xs rounded-full flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
          SYSTEM_STATUS: SECURE
        </span>

        <span class="text-on-surface-variant font-label-xs text-label-xs uppercase tracking-widest">
          Case ID: 771-NX-24
        </span>

      </div>

      <h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg text-on-surface mb-6">
        MFT Anomaly Detection in NTFS Vol_01
      </h1>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start gap-y-4 gap-x-8 py-6 border-y border-outline-variant">

        <!-- Author -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">

          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high border border-outline-variant flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD-LdoukxPesgYXIhKPEcUzhBVKqZKJp03yBtkFeQ34ohc0tjRv4h8y-8SKifSG9-tu3gRhMtcRW_uwWfdluL9gNu8-guNta1vunGh7FXR9XrtWaQNxa3uW3_em_6CT4NsSWKu9TU7df84tglAR6ugtFk8p1m42julgAd2PJDBpu6SzkQS2mCXgmmbslfhMQzX3U3z8IvCePOsdpngDOVReZYvegqGfcxsMFXV-5OtnYnjK8EVps_VIaQspbfAzwT0wbwnWqLFG9UY"
              alt="author" />
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-label-xs text-label-xs text-on-surface-variant">AUTHOR</p>
            <p class="font-code-sm text-code-sm text-primary">Santo-Ryu</p>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Timestamp -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-label-xs text-label-xs text-on-surface-variant">TIMESTAMP</p>
          <p class="font-code-sm text-code-sm text-on-surface">2024.05.12 14:02 UTC</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Category -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-label-xs text-label-xs text-on-surface-variant">CATEGORY</p>
          <p class="font-code-sm text-code-sm text-primary">#file-system-forensics</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Actions -->
        <div class="ml-auto flex gap-2">

          <button class="p-2 border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">bookmark</span>
          </button>

          <button class="p-2 border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">print</span>
          </button>

        </div>

      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="markdown-content font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">
        

      <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant font-medium italic mb-8 border-l-4 border-primary/40 pl-6 py-2">
        Abstract: Investigation of $MFT structure variations indicative of anti-forensics timestamp manipulation or unauthorized record injection within a standard NTFS volume.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-headline-md uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">
        Introduction to $MFT Structures
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-6">
        The Master File Table ($MFT) is the heart of the NTFS file system...
      </p>

      <!-- Alert -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-high border border-primary/20 p-6 my-8 flex gap-4 items-start">

        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">warning</span>

        <div>
          <p class="font-code-sm text-primary font-bold mb-1 uppercase tracking-wider">
            Forensic Warning
          </p>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant m-0">
            Unauthorized modification of $MFT records can lead to system instability...
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <h2 class="font-headline-md uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">
        Automated Analysis Script
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-4">
        To streamline the identification of record gaps...
      </p>

      <!-- Code Block -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant my-8 overflow-hidden rounded">

        <div class="bg-surface-variant px-4 py-2 border-b border-outline-variant flex justify-between items-center">
          <span class="font-code-sm">&gt;_ log_analysis.py</span>

          <button class="text-primary hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 font-code-sm"
            onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(`def parse_mft(path):
    with open(path, 'rb') as f:
        while (chunk := f.read(1024)):
            if chunk[:4] != b'FILE':
                print(f'Anomaly detected at {f.tell()}')`)">

            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">content_copy</span>
            Copy
          </button>
        </div>

        <pre class="p-6 font-code-sm text-primary-container overflow-x-auto">
        <code set:html={`def parse_mft(path):
            with open(path, 'rb') as f:
                while (chunk := f.read(1024)):
                    if chunk[:4] != b'FILE':
                        print(f'Anomaly detected at {f.tell()}')`} />
        </pre>

      </div>

      <h2 class="font-headline-md uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">
        Key Indicators of Compromise
      </h2>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-10">
        <li>$STANDARD_INFORMATION vs $FILE_NAME timestamp mismatch</li>
        <li>Unusually large record numbers in system files</li>
        <li>USA mismatch at sector boundaries</li>
        <li>Non-standard MFT header flags</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Image -->
      <figure class="my-12">

        <div class="relative w-full aspect-video border border-outline-variant overflow-hidden group">

          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD61beTVpK6e9cgiYflGvEgaQlwzKhPy_7yNkD7JWjuEu1tVbJXoms7yaXZg_HoB19E1LKzrq_WWKeeCxVnySHGEDLiUkO3WiH9LCiCXmPpQ34SnDf1VSXGpWpRJJsWb23ojsqr0tsHHvcJ0sE7YzNA1_LQmWGKbkqpb-C-hhEOO_CVsxTllUb0Mql7lD14aO4O28SdyGK8FV-CEG66P-h4fj-GK1kNEF4J6XkUwghRrv5VpmnOBlOaW_GeLt17zja-YHKOIhX85Vw"
            alt="hex view" />

          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5"></div>

        </div>

        <figcaption class="mt-4 text-center text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
          Fig 1.1: Raw Hex View of MFT Record 442
        </figcaption>

      </figure>

      <h2 class="font-headline-md uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">
        Conclusion
      </h2>

      <p>
        The anomalies strongly suggest deliberate record manipulation...
      </p>

    </section>

    <!-- Footer Navigation -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-outline-variant flex justify-between items-center">

      <a class="group" href="#">
        <div class="text-primary flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
          Previous
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="group text-right" href="#">
        <div class="text-primary flex items-center gap-2 justify-end group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">
          Next
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>

  </article>

  <!-- Sidebar -->
  <aside class="lg:col-span-4 hidden lg:block">

    <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-8">

      <!-- TOC -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant p-6">

        <h3 class="font-headline-md uppercase text-sm mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">list_alt</span>
          Table of Contents
        </h3>

        <nav class="space-y-3 text-sm">

          <a class="block text-primary border-l-2 border-primary pl-4">01. Introduction</a>
          <a class="block text-on-surface-variant pl-4">02. Scripting</a>
          <a class="block text-on-surface-variant pl-4">03. Indicators</a>
          <a class="block text-on-surface-variant pl-4">04. Hex View</a>
          <a class="block text-on-surface-variant pl-4">05. Conclusion</a>

        </nav>

      </div>

      <!-- Share -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant p-6">

        <h3 class="font-headline-md uppercase text-sm mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">share</span>
          Share
        </h3>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">

          <button class="border p-3">EMAIL</button>
          <button class="border p-3">LINK</button>
          <button class="border p-3">PDF</button>
          <button class="border p-3">RSS</button>

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </aside>

</div>